    "transliteration": "ALLAAHUMMA WAFFIR FEEHE HAZZEE MIN BARAKA'TEHI WA SAHHIL SABEELEE ELAA KHAYRAATEHI WA LAA TAHRIMNEE QABOOLA HASANAATEHI YAA HAADEYAN ELAL HAQQIL MOBEENE.", 
    "english": "O Allah, on this day, (please) save me a share of its blessings, make easy my way to the obtainment of its goodness, and do not deprive me of Your approval of the good deeds (that I do on this day). O He Who guides to the evident truth!"
